Build-time binaries (NOT stored in this repository)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

android/app/src/main/assets/ggml-hexagon/libggml-htp-v*.so
  Qualcomm Hexagon (HTP) backend libraries for ggml/llama.cpp. These are NOT
  committed to this repo — llama.rn's Gradle copies them from its package
  (node_modules/llama.rn/bin/arm64-v8a) into the app's assets at build time, and
  the path is git-ignored. They let llama.cpp offload to a Qualcomm Snapdragon
  NPU; on other SoCs (e.g. Google Tensor) they are unused and inference falls
  back to CPU. See llama.rn and llama.cpp (MIT) below.

